race.comment: KATE'S TIARA (2) is racing in great heart against far better fields than this. Came from last of six to get up for second last start in a Class 6 over 1000m at the Sunshine Coast. Crying out for 1200m now and in this far easier race she is clearly the one to beat. NIGHT FIGHTER (5) won in this grade over 1400m at Coonabarabran two runs ago. Found the line well subsequently in open company at Armidale. Poses a serious threat back in this more suitable contest. MY MATE KATE (9) was plain last start at the second run of the campaign, beaten comfortably over 1100m at this track. Has won none from 11 in the first two runs of her preps, but two from four third-up. Watch for a spike in form. CANNY PROSPECT (3) is in tremendous form. Had an eight-week let-up before thundering home to grab second in a strong form race over 1106m at Port Macquarie last start. Kept fresh again and is one to watch for late in the piece. NYALI SANDS (8) is a good fresh performer worth including off a short break.
